  <brief_title>Wearable Pulsed Electromagnetic Fields Device in Knee Osteoarthritis: Double Blinded, Randomized Clinical Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Wearable Pulsed Electromagnetic Fields Device in Knee Osteoarthritis Patients: a Double Blinded, Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
